{"tid":469008,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄國防部貼電玩遊戲截圖　「力證」美國支援IS","createTime":"2017-11-15T01:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T12:17:39.000Z","uid":20058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"25e37a10edc041ed2dcb0812cd06b535b52f6a0a","tid":469008,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T01:50:12.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯國防部周二（14日）於官方Facebook帳戶，圖文並茂指有證據證明美國在中東地區援助回教極端組織「伊斯蘭國」（IS）。但網友其後迅速發現，俄羅斯公布的照片全都是過去兩年的影片中剪輯下來，其中有一張更是電玩遊戲的截圖。 <br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯國防部聲稱於上周四（9日），在敘利亞和伊拉克邊境所拍攝到一批黑白照片，並指這次行動「確定了美國領導的聯盟，為IS提供了直接合作和援助的事實」。不過有眼利的網民發現，其中一張照片和電玩遊戲「AC-130 Gunship Simulator」，於2015年3月上載至互聯網的畫面完全相同。 <br />\n<br />\n國防部事後已刪除帖文，但克里姆林宮就對此事隻字不提。俄羅斯官媒塔斯社（TASS）引述國防部消息人士指，事件是緣於局內一名職員錯誤地上傳了這些圖像所致，並正就事件調查是那一位職員出錯。不過俄羅斯國防部強調他們的指控真實。五角大樓則回應指俄羅斯的指控只是一大堆謊話。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171115/mobile/bknint-20171115062109212-1115_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171115%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20171115062109212-1115_17011_001.html&d=dVuD9CyTRKGt4QCszSyEAvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=ef70bd88\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171115/mobile/bknint-20171115062109212-1115_17011_001.html</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52337a2edc36389efd486c950a772ec98badb426","tid":469008,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T01:54:02.000Z","msg":"柒到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0347a81eb5ea0afc5d6bb549867f6de5dfd7cb3","tid":469008,"uid":67346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T01:59:06.000Z","msg":"嗰位人兄依家係咪係西伯利亞捉緊魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5678223054b59c02c1968ece8ca3011ed0cc8dc3","tid":469008,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T02:02:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嗰位人兄依家係咪係西伯利亞捉緊魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係捉咗去西伯利亞餵魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883bcdd5919f29ec4a3437ec0bc032e9126db940","tid":469008,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:17:39.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯個政府有冇咁ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}